<%= image_tag(@story.image) %>

<h2><%= @story.title %></h2>
<p>Hello, <%= @story.name %>. I hope you enjoy your journey to <%= @story.town %>. This is just the beginning.</p>


<p><%= link_to "Delete this story", story_path(@story), method: :delete, data: { confirm: "Are you sure you want to delete this story?" } %> </p>